        h2 Get '/employer/employerID/:policies'
            p Route returns a list of policies under a specific employer by their id
            p Route: http://localhost:1337/employer/employerID/:policies
            p Expected Output: '[{ ID: 25, Employer Name: 'RadioShack' Coverage Type: 'STD' Funding: 'List Bill' Policy Number: 2548, Policy EDOC: 01-01-1980}]'
